# Google Maps JavaScript API key — used by the Spaces explorer map (src/screens/SpacesExplorer.jsx)
# 1. Create a key in Google Cloud Console
# 2. Enable the "Maps JavaScript API"
# 3. Restrict the key to your domain(s) for production
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the value:
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
